VI want to give you guys three questions
p99
aVthat will help you be able to spot some bad statistics.
p100
aVSo, question number one is: Can you see uncertainty?
p101
aVOne of things that's really changed people's relationship with numbers,
p102
aVand even their trust in the media,
p103
aVhas been the use of political polls.
p104
aVI personally have a lot of issues with political polls
p105
aVbecause I think the role of journalists is actually to report the facts
p106
